      "content": "That's a strong start, very intense. To make it feel even more authentic to the period, can you expand on the specific reasons why he views them as \"primitive\"? Like, maybe he mentions their lack of technology or their social structures compared to Europe, to really hammer home why he thinks they need British guidance to become \"civilized\"?",
